page.title: 18FASHIONS OF 1985
page.content: The jeans used to be baggy on people a few years ago, but now they are tighter. People also wear leg warmers around thier ankles. Some fashion boots have pointed tips. Pixy boots have a pointed end and they have a piece of leather that comes up your legs. The makeup is very nice. Eye shadow comes in different shades of pink, blue, silver, gold, green and lots of other colours. There are some good lipsticks as well. They are mainly reds and pinks. You can also buy blusher, glitter to put in your hair and face, eye liner, foundation cream, and many others.
